{"tid":955643,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【二手劈價】麗城花園望海3房700萬沽　呎價跌穿1萬元","createTime":"2018-12-25T14:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T06:10:59.000Z","uid":174649,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f30a1d0556840697c99aed9a18b83d2388d44bfb","tid":955643,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:38:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181225/large/1545719953_9a3b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181225%2Flarge%2F1545719953_9a3b.jpg&h=3db34192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聖誕假期前夕新盤熱賣，凍結二手購買力，減價成交持續。美聯物業李杏儀表示，荃灣麗城花園3期2座低層E室3房向海戶，實用面積728方呎，劈近200萬元，以700萬元沽出，呎價僅9,615元，跌穿一萬大關。屋苑同期1座中層E室，11月曾以860萬元沽出，與是次成交價比較，跌約18.6%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n李補充，原業主叫價880萬元，放盤逾半年未獲承接，最終減價約兩成，終獲區內客斥資700萬元承接，<strong>呎價約9,615元</strong>。原業主於1995年8月以約266.8萬元購入上述物業，是次轉售賬面賺433.2萬元，升值逾1.6倍。"},{"pid":"871480792a01fa8439d4a0193b50fe90606fb218","tid":955643,"uid":78791,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:42:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d9a178f650a8194bb1125706fbe40da2e508bde","tid":955643,"uid":37599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:47:37.000Z","msg":"聖誕快落<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新年快快落<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"665046cd60ec6c96ff9bbb2aae551363783e8800","tid":955643,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T14:53:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d69426321d93b6bc08789467737286c0f81ef461","tid":955643,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"終於劈到荃灣"},{"pid":"fea2242c6419b92544cc6b3307d79a0843b145cd","tid":955643,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:02:30.000Z","msg":"柏傲灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ca4dc6816b66866434dce5ec27b58467fa7601","tid":955643,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:02:38.000Z","msg":"仲賺400個<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea66b157d5fbbe62007166489bbb36c5239d5ac6","tid":955643,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2bd4af472efd363f800c6f4457e503496365d219","tid":955643,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:07:33.000Z","msg":"唱淡樓市做乜，咩居心呀"},{"pid":"a39e8daab900225fa0156ac5c4e8a979f7b8f5e7","tid":955643,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"高位1010萬 (不過係中層)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2018年08月02<br />\n【本報訊】二手樓價續創新高。中原呂宗霖表示，新房策推出後，二手成交氣氛略為回落，不過樓價繼續於高位企穩。荃灣麗城花園7月共錄得10宗成交，包括剛誕下首宗千萬樓王成交，為3期1座中層H室，實用728方呎，三房套房間隔，向南享海景，獲換樓客以1,010萬元承接，樓價創屋苑新高，呎價13,874元。原業主2012年以550萬元買入單位，持貨六年獲利460萬元，升值84%。"},{"pid":"ceef6066bf5f1cb9c27c254fa8cc3e8c1f5f9e75","tid":955643,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:17:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b6715b6626d600b4762508c285db37c2c0f26403","tid":955643,"uid":37599,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"a39e8daab900225fa0156ac5c4e8a979f7b8f5e7","tid":955643,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-25T15:11:13.000Z","msg":"高位1010萬 (不過係中層)  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2018年08月02<br />\n【本報訊】二手樓價續創新高。中原呂宗霖表示，新房策推出後，二手成交氣氛略為回落，不過樓價繼續於高位企穩。荃灣麗城花園7月共錄得10宗成交，包括剛誕下首宗千萬樓王成交，為3期1座中層H室，實用728方呎，三房套房間隔，向南享海景，獲換樓客以1,010萬元承接，樓價創屋苑新高，呎價